Splenectomized or nonsplenectomized subjects with a primary diagnosis of ITP from either of
the phase 3 studies (20030105 or 20030212) or the open-label extension study 20030213;
pretreatment bone marrow biopsy within 1 year of enrollment into the phase 3 study;
separate written informed consent for the follow-up bone marrow.
